title: A Look Ahead To Monterey Car Week
itunes:title: A Look Ahead To Monterey Car Week
description:
Dave Magers, CEO of Mecum Auctions, discusses the record-setting collector car market. Nick Frelinghuysen, Managing Director and Portfolio Manager of Equities at Chilton Trust, talks markets and investing. Janet Elkin, CEO of ICON Medical Network, discusses vaccine access and healthcare staffing. Brent Schutte, Chief Investment Strategist at Northwestern Mutual Wealth Management Company, talks markets. Hosted by Paul Sweeney and Matt Miller. (Kailey Leinz fills in for Paul Sweeney)
